          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1657730609581-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Using clean hands, combine <strong>half</strong> of the<strong> ras el hanout </strong>(save the rest for later!) and the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> in a large bowl<strong> </strong>with the <strong>lamb mince </strong>and <strong>diced onion</strong></p><p>Season<strong> </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>then mix thoroughly until well combined – this is your <strong>spiced lamb mixture</strong></p><p>Shape the <strong>spiced lamb mixture</strong> into 1 <span class=\"text-danger\">[2] </span>loaf<span class=\"text-danger\">[ves]</span></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1657730611828-x200.jpg",
