            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>hazelnuts </strong>and <strong>cumin seeds </strong>to a<strong> pestle & mortar </strong>and grind until roughly ground</p><p>Tip: Don't have a pestle & mortar? Chop roughly instead!</p><p>Add the <strong>ground hazelnuts & cumin seeds</strong> to a plate and fully coat the loaf<span class=\"text-danger\">[ves]</span></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
