    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>coated loaf<span class=\"text-danger\">[ves]</span></strong> to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 30-35 min or until the meatloaf<span class=\"text-danger\">[ves]</span> are cooked through – this is your <strong>hazelnut crusted lamb meatloaf</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p>",
